 Player: Look, Mariam asked me to save the kids from Svarog. Do you really want that guy''s "guests" to get ''em?
 
 Rebel Leader: No. I guess our goals are the same for now. We''ll help you get the children back, but we''re doing it for Tollana.
 
 Player: Whatever. Here comes the Patrol.', 0, 0);


 Machra: That''s me. Oh. [Player name]. This a friend of yours?
 Bench: I am. My name is Bench, I work with [Player Name] in with Op-CORE. My colleagues would appreciate knowing a bit more about our powerful allies.
 Machra: They would, would they?
 Bench: Absolutely! Alliances with powerful individuals like yourself help our organization immensely.
 Machra: Well I am the most powerful Lucian on Tollana.
 Bench: Exactly! And who better to tell us more about our allies the Lucians than yourself.
 Machra: Ask away Mr. Bench.
 Bench: Thank you, sir! So.', 0, 0);

 Machra: If you''d like to speak to other Lucians on Tollana, go right ahead. 
 Bench: Thank you, sir!
 Machra: My friends call me Machra.
 Bench: Thank you Machra.
 Machra: [Player name] I like the people you work with. They''re smart. They know good business when they see it. Tell you what, I''ll give you a discount.
 ', 0, 0);

