 Player: Yes, ma''am.
 Travell: I think we can begin by-
 Rinak: Councilmember Travell.
 Travell: Councilmember Rinak.
 Rinak: Councilmember, who is this?
 Travell: [Player name] is here representing Op-CORE.
 Rinak: I''d welcome you to Tollana but you seem to have made yourself at home, [Player name]. While I applaud Council member Travell''s eagerness to improve our situation, I must apologize. Councilmember Travell has spoken out of turn. Please inform your superiors that all future communications with the Curia will go through me', 0, 0);

 Player: Yes Ma''am
 Coppelman: Ideas?
 Player: Bench seemed to charm the Lucians. We could send him to schmooze Rinak while we work with Travell. 
 Coppelman: Excellent idea, Soldier. Here''s another thought. Get some bugs from Zuritska. Plant them while Rinak is busy with Bench. I''d like to keep a closer eye on the Curia.', 0, 0);

 Player: Councilmember. This is Mr. Bench. He''s been assigned to act as an Ambassador for Op-CORE. Bench? This is councilmember Rinak.
 Bench: A pleasure to meet you Councilmember Rinak.
 Player: Captain Coppelmann also wanted me to give this token of support.
 Rinak: Thank you. 
 Bench: Sir, I''d like to express my admiration for the Tollan people.', 0, 0);

 Player: Yes Ma''am.
